{"tid":836910,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［官宣］摩連奴已在雙方同意下解約","createTime":"2018-09-26T03:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T13:41:57.000Z","uid":46911,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"080fc2f8e0e53efa114ed347ded608569cd87bf3","tid":836910,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"英超球會車路士宣佈，在雙方同意下與領隊摩連奴解約。<br />\n<br />\n今年52歲的葡萄牙人摩連奴，帶領車路士奪得上季英超冠軍，但今屆幾肯定無望衛冕，要打進前四也甚難，因為今季出戰16場，表現惡劣，僅勝出4場，輸掉9場，上周以1:2不敵李斯特城後，現僅排第16位，距離降班區1分。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴201年3回歸英超，第二次執教車路士。兩次領軍共為球會贏得3次英超、1次足總盃和3次聯賽盃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/114615_44b40ffca3e640552313fe12dba935e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F114615_44b40ffca3e640552313fe12dba935e1.png&h=11c813bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支持永續摩帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1418d170a206739d1368dc462e0a95cb1d515f43","tid":836910,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c015f6cd52915a1b591317faca512e0708632d0f","tid":836910,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a024023528cc19809e1d56656e66e4b505f51b97","tid":836910,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a2abe5529627742a78b7dd39b390cabe011d01","tid":836910,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"明知